{"tid":819486,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"丁珮驚爆第三春戀嫩版李小龍？","createTime":"2018-09-14T23:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T05:56:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"99b9b7813e5d37f664fe6d3df12ce0cac56b3cf7","tid":819486,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T23:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BpgTBF65OqO031jBb12Z9w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/b2415f28943ef4f8ac3b42a299d19bbc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBpgTBF65OqO031jBb12Z9w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fb2415f28943ef4f8ac3b42a299d19bbc&h=1cf1fb28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PZfX21KMNDS__kSyxcSmCA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/9746b4aceba38b40704bd9f26a89bf6d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPZfX21KMNDS__kSyxcSmCA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F9746b4aceba38b40704bd9f26a89bf6d&h=2a9d5a40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已故一代巨星李小龍的紅顏知己丁珮，淡出影壇十多年，近日被揭有「第三春」，有人目睹她早前在大嶼山拜大佛時拖着一名貌似李小龍的男士，兩人表現親暱步上石梯，消息震驚娛圈！<br />\n<br />\n一代宗師李小龍離世46年，但有關其傳聞依然不絕，最近有消息指，其生前紅顏知己、現年71歲的丁珮覓得「第三春」，而新歡樣貌更與李小龍十分相似。有人拍下二人同遊大嶼山寶蓮禪寺的視頻，兩人邊行邊傾步上長長石梯，狀甚親密，可惜片中只見丁珮側面，而嫩版李小龍只聞其聲，未有出鏡。<br />\n<br />\n美籍華人闖影壇<br />\n記者追查下終於找到這位貌似李小龍的男士，原來是美籍華人，名叫江學賢，從小視李小龍為偶像，更苦練對方的招牌功夫雙節棍。由於樣貌酷似李小龍，故被星探睇中，進軍美國影視圈。記者追問江學賢與丁珮關係，他解釋是因搜集偶像生平故事而結緣，聚會都是為更了解李小龍，加上因常與「李小龍基金會」合作，故亦與李小龍女兒李香凝結成好友。<br />\n<br />\n開戲揭武林秘史<br />\n由於李小龍的粉絲每年都會舉行活動悼念偶像，今年更特別熱鬧，如被封迷你版李小龍的日本童星今井竜惺早前曾來港獻技向偶像致敬，故江學賢決定將李小龍鮮為人知的一段武林秘史搬上大銀幕，他說：「故事以當年李小龍與亞洲腿王譚道良立下生死狀的決戰為骨幹，演員方面已邀請丁珮、李香凝、譚道良與兒子父子兵上陣，還有李小龍的銀幕情人苗可秀等演出，很多謝前輩丁珮給予不少意見，希望能拍出一部大家都喜歡看的電影。」"},{"pid":"41116077a61960b338a6103deb62a1ce5d166526","tid":819486,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"以為係贏國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ee835865281eba39ba60d9ec2fe43d75286ea5","tid":819486,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41116077a61960b338a6103deb62a1ce5d166526","tid":819486,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"以為係贏國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"你指丁珮？"},{"pid":"382d80b1ebab5f8a144ae7cd09bd8a6e3275266f","tid":819486,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37ee835865281eba39ba60d9ec2fe43d75286ea5","tid":819486,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41116077a61960b338a6103deb62a1ce5d166526","tid":819486,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"以為係贏國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"你指丁珮？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"個假李小龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贏國都成日有人扮"}]}